Revision history for Linux-Event-Stream

0.001  2026-02-22
  - Initial release.
  - Buffered write path with partial write handling and automatic write arming/disarming.
  - High/low watermark backpressure state (is_write_blocked) and buffered_bytes.
  - Raw on_read callback with pause_read/resume_read.
  - close_after_drain for graceful shutdown.
  - Idempotent close and on_close lifecycle callback.
